Uses of Package
com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.operation

  • Packages that use com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.operation 
    Package Description
    com.fasterxml.clustermate.client
    Main public types for ClusterMate client module; most important of which is NetworkClient that is the object application code uses to access data in the logical distributed Store.
    com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.operation
    Package that contains abstractions used for handling of logical operations that may consist of multiple physical (HTTP) calls.
  • Classes in com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.operation used by com.fasterxml.clustermate.client 
    Class and Description
    DeleteOperationResult 
    GetOperationResult
    OperationResult subtype used with GET operations, adds actual result (of type T which is type of GetContentProcessor passed to call).
    HeadOperationResult 
    OperationConfig 
    PutOperationResult 
    StoreEntryLister
    Value class that is used as result type for content list operation.
